  "stem": "<p>A museum rents tablets to visitors. The museum earns revenue of <math alttext=\"dollar sign 14\"><mo>$</mo><mn>14</mn>\n</math> for each tablet rented for the day. On Wednesday, the museum earned <math alttext=\"dollar sign 406\"><mo>$</mo><mn>406</mn>\n</math> in profit from renting tablets after paying daily expenses of <math alttext=\"dollar sign 112\"><mo>$</mo><mn>112</mn>\n</math>. How many tablets did the museum rent on Wednesday? <math alttext=\"left parenthesis profit equals total revenue minus total expenses right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mtext>profit</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>total</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>revenue</mtext><mo>&#8722;</mo><mtext>total</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>expenses</mtext></mrow></mfenced></math></p>",
